      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "JUST A BABE (1) was safely held last time out, finishing fifth at Broken Hill over 525m behind Croydon (30.85) in a NG. Solid formlines coming through her last run. Should be very hard to beat this time. GIGGLIN' (4) stalked the lead but wound up strongly to score (30.77) at this track in Grade 6 over 530m. Solid formlines coming through her last run. Should feature again. DOLAN (8) is rarely out of the finish, recording 28 places from 52 starts. Finished third (31.26) at this track last time making it two minors on end. Solid record at the distance winning three races. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card last start despite being beaten. Expected to be in this for a long way. ZIPPING NORRIS (6) placed here at this trip last start - cannot be ignored.",
